	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然是這樣！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
