	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才、<delay20 /><20_2 arg="1" /><delay8 /><anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />才沒有那種事呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這、<delay20 />這只是<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
