	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說，你美得都讓人看入神了呢。<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
