<anim id="Hesitate" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">最近用手機之類的產品看書的人，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
好像越來越多了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我果然還是比較喜歡紙本的書呢。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我懂<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />你說的那種感覺。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
