<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有活版印刷字才有的凹凹凸凸的感覺，<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的非常讓人著迷呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我懂<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />你說的那種感覺。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是自己喜歡的作家寫的小說，<delay20 />
