	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是這樣！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不僅是初版的書，<delay20 />還有再版、<delay8 /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
