	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是這樣！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以和封面一起欣賞的還有書腰喔！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />書腰上還有對這本書的評論，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我每次拿到新書都很期待呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />感覺這是只有內行人才懂的，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />享受讀書樂趣的方式呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
你看起來總是那麼沉穩，真讓人羨慕呢。<anim id="Hello" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><10_4 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你平常會特別注意什麼嗎？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想……<20_2 arg="3" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都會注意舉手投足間要從容，<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
