	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<20_2 arg="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />原來如此。<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總是<delay20 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一緊張就手忙腳亂的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
你有沒有遇過<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />覺得很慌張的時候呢？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然有呀<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" />！<delay frames="40" />
