	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使內心<20_2 arg="4" />波濤洶湧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />也要冷靜嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺對我來說好像很難做到呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那請問<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
