<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也會更接近自己理想中，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />女性沉穩的樣子<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">如果這點小事<20_2 arg="3" />能幫上你的忙，<delay8 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請儘管用。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
